      <description>&lt;p&gt;Track Tally is best used as an App installed to your Home Screen.
Follow the steps below to install&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#install-on-android&#34;&gt;Install on Android&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#install-on-iphone&#34;&gt;Install on iPhone&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;install-on-android&#34;&gt;Install on Android&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click on the three dots (1) in your browser and choose &amp;ldquo;Add to Home Screen (2)&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;




  
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://tracktally.github.io/doc/install/android-add-to-homescreen_hu_82b6a5cf3e448c0a.png&#34; alt=&#34;Android Add to Home Screen&#34;&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;install-on-iphone&#34;&gt;Install on iPhone&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Follow the sequence 1 - 4 below to add the App to your Home Screen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;



  
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://tracktally.github.io/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen1_hu_8dd01e08d39843e4.png&#34; alt=&#34;Add to Home Screen&#34;&gt;





  
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://tracktally.github.io/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen2_hu_a09c3b44c71adee9.png&#34; alt=&#34;Add to Home Screen&#34;&gt;





  
  &lt;img src=&#34;https://tracktally.github.io/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen3_hu_8e8fc49d623f87c7.png&#34; alt=&#34;Add to Home Screen&#34;&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Track Tally is best used as an App installed to your Home Screen.
Follow the steps below to install</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="#install-on-android">Install on Android</a></li>
<li><a href="#install-on-iphone">Install on iPhone</a></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="install-on-android">Install on Android</h4>
<p>Click on the three dots (1) in your browser and choose &ldquo;Add to Home Screen (2)&rdquo;.</p>




  
  <img src="/doc/install/android-add-to-homescreen_hu_82b6a5cf3e448c0a.png" alt="Android Add to Home Screen">

<h4 id="install-on-iphone">Install on iPhone</h4>
<p>Follow the sequence 1 - 4 below to add the App to your Home Screen.</p>
<p>



  
  <img src="/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen1_hu_8dd01e08d39843e4.png" alt="Add to Home Screen">





  
  <img src="/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen2_hu_a09c3b44c71adee9.png" alt="Add to Home Screen">





  
  <img src="/doc/install/ios-add-to-homescreen3_hu_8e8fc49d623f87c7.png" alt="Add to Home Screen">
</p>
